2. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the dutch##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | card-games | singing    |
| Beverage           | fanta  | lemonade |
| Nationality   | dutch      | spanish    |

